replies.author: 吕易天
replies.txt_content:
未知的依赖异常：dynmap
DynmapPlotMe需要dynmap才能够被加载。

replies.author: 白羊羊
replies.txt_content: DynmapPlotMe这个插件有问题，你可以试试看重新下载安装
